@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp((v0 / (v2 + 0.83 - v2 + 0.13)))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.cos((tmp + 0.93 / tmp + 0.01)))
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.30 / v1 + 0.85) * wp.cos(tmp + 0.57)) / wp.sin(wp.sin(tmp + 0.44)))
    v1 = 0.15
    v2 = wp.abs((0.24 * (tmp + 0.13 * tmp + 0.45)))
    v0 = wp.cos(((v0 + 0.66 + v0 + 0.32) - v1))
    v0 = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.17) / (v1 + 0.22 + v0 + 0.19)) * ((v1 + 0.66 / v0 + 0.79) + (v1 + 0.79 / v2 + 0.46)))
    data[tid] = v0
